messages.content: ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite is an extension for ComfyUI that enables the composition of text and images in creative ways. It is currently under development, as indicated by 'WIP' in the provided documentation.
What feature was integrated from the contribution by @h3clikejava?
The contribution by @h3clikejava added an arc-shaped text layout feature to ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite, which is considered very cool.
Is the documentation for ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite completed?
No, the documentation for ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite is not yet completed, as indicated by '说明还在写……' in the provided documentation.
Are there any images showing the arc-shaped text layout feature?

Yes, there is an image in the documentation that demonstrates the arc-shaped text layout feature, which is referenced by the link '![Dingtalk_20231218214037](https://github.com/ZHO-ZHO-ZHO/ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite/assets/140084057/070c0cda-60ff-43c4-9941-92074d6f9602)'.
Are there any other extensions similar to ComfyUI-Text_Image-Composite?
Yes, there are other extensions listed in the documentation, such as Allor and MTB, which contribute to the functionality of ComfyUI.
